channel.description: What do you study on school let me know ;) well I live in Belgium and study social and technical sciences what I hate the most? math and grammar And I'm almost Donne with exams (yes , I wanna know some more of the study mechanism in the other country's) these where my exams. *natural sciences (Biology,Cemestry,Physics) [good] * Social Science (=Psychology) [good] *Maths[+-] *Dutch[good] *French[enorm bad :(] *Geography[good] *History[Very good] *independent work [+-] *English[good] *IT [good] Thats it.

Period 1: AP Physics

Period 3: AP Spanish
Period 4: AP Statistics

[/quote]
